heading: Whispering Pines Dungeon Guide
content: Whispering Pines is a good dungeon with a good aspect for Earth Druids, the . The slay all enemies objective keeps this dungeon from being top tier, although it does have spiders in the earlier half of the dungeon, so don't overlook this one at least for the Renown rewards if nothing else. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
